.TH SIGNBIT 2
.SH NAME
signbit, copysign  \- sign of floating point
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B #include <u.h>
.br
.B #include <libc.h>
.PP
.nf
.B
int signbit(double x)
.PP
.B
double copysign(double x, double y)
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I Signbit
returns true if the value of
.IR x
has its sign bit set, otherwise it returns false.
.PP
.I Copysign
returns a value whose magnitude is taken from
.IR x
and whose sign is taken from
.IR y .
.SH SOURCE
.BR /sys/src/libc/port/signbit.c
.SH HISTORY
.I Signbit
and
.I copysign
appeared in December, 2019.
